Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.26,0:04:40.34,对话-CN-V2,,0,0,0,,麗奈\N{\fs40\fnjf-openhuninn-2.0\b1}{\fs40\fnjf-openhuninn-2.0\b1}ねぇ　麗奈
