Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:16.24,对话-CN-V2,,0,0,0,,我會加油的\N{\fs40\fnjf-openhuninn-2.0\b1}{\fs40\fnjf-openhuninn-2.0\b1}がんばる！
