Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:20.88,对话-CN-V2,,0,0,0,,我之後會把資料給你\N{\fs40\fnjf-openhuninn-2.0\b1}{\fs40\fnjf-openhuninn-2.0\b1}あとで資料を渡す
